Focus management is a strategic approach to optimizing employee productivity and well-being by enhancing attention, reducing distractions, and prioritizing tasks 
effectively. It involves techniques and policies that help individuals and teams maintain concentration on high-value activities, ultimately leading to improved 
performance and job satisfaction.
